The paper discusses the design and architecture of secure vehicular communication systems, which involves topics related to computer security (cs.CR), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), software engineering (cs.SE), control systems (cs.SY), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The focus on security and privacy also suggests that cs.CR and cs.NI are the most likely categories.
